Quote:  <i>Polyprion americanus</i> Bloch and Schneider. This deep-water representative of the genus is now identified by Waite ... with the wreck-fish of the Atlantic. It is occasionally taken outside Otago Heads, and is known by the local fishermen as `bass groper' or `black bass'.
Notes:  Thomson, Otago)
